name: "here and now" - HAN inspired generative art piece
description:
this piece was created using the NightCafe Studio "text to image" AI tool. i fed the AI my 1/1 liasomething ticket (https://objkt.com/asset/hicetnunc/367421) from Here and Now 3 by @WideAwakeBeets 

I want to mint this piece as a thank you to Liasomething and Beets for their inspiring work. I will give this piece away to anyone who is holding a Here and Now ticket. (http://wideawakeprojects.com/hereandnow/) I highly recommend you go check out what Beets has created with Here and Now, the art, the project, the community is truly something special. 

*THIS IS NOT A TICKET FOR HERE AND NOW*
